title: Waves - Tuner Full v0.9.4
description:
Waves - Tuner Full v0.9.4 Apk - The popular gStrings chromatic tuner app rewritten
from scratch with a multi-core optimized engine, improved fundamental frequency detection,
smooth OpenGL graphics a redesigned UX and a simplistic/focused holo UI.

The app measures sound pitch using your phone's microphone, letting you tune any musical
instrument (violin,viola,violoncello,bass,guitar.ukulele,piano even wind instruments to name a few that have been tested).

Updated: September 8, 2013
Current Version: 0.9.4
Requires Android: 2.3 And Up
Category: Music & Audio
Size: 503kb
